#

Crispy Chicken Sandwich

35 min
$12
650 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

glutendairy

Dietary Tags:

high-proteincomfort-food

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

sandwichchickenfried

Description

Enjoy a crispy chicken sandwich with a crunchy coating and fresh toppings, perfect for a satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • boneless chicken thighs: 2 pieces
  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • buttermilk: 1 cup
  • bread crumbs: 1 cup
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • onion powder: 1 teaspoon
  • vegetable oil: for frying
  • burger buns: 2 pieces
  • lettuce: 2 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • pickles: 4 slices
  • mayonnaise: 2 tablespoons
